<td class=\"attr-right\">THOUSANDS OF LIGHTS: This amazing fire stick fire starter survival tool holds 2ml of lighter fluid (not included) and will ignite over 15,000 times, never leaving you without a fire or heat source</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">PORTABLE AND LIGHTWEIGHT: Attached to an included keychain, the emergency match lighter fire stick is easily transportable and lightweight; secure it alongside your keys or on a lanyard, on a backpack strap or loop, with a carabiner or toss it in your bug out bag or survival kit</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">EASY TO USE: Simply pull the fire stick starter out of the casing; the lighter survival tool will start a fire every time you strike the magnesium fire stick against the outer aluminum striking plate just like you would do using a regular match</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">SPECIFICATIONS: Weight: 0.5lbs; Dimensions: 2.5 x 0.75 inches; Magnesium Rod: 1.25 inches; Fuel: Lighter fluid; Fuel capacity: 2ml; NOTE: lighter fluid NOT included due to shipping restrictions</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t  </table>\n\t\t\t  </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t  </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t  <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t  <p>&copy; 2024</p>\n\t\t  </div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t      </div> <!-- /container -->\n              <div style=\"clear:both\">\n              <table>&nbsp;</table>\n              </div>\n  </body>\n</html> <center><a href=\"https://pages.ebay.com/seller-center/listing/listing-advanced-sellers/third-party-listing-tools.html#third-party-listing-tools\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=0 width=88 height=33 src=\"https://secureimages.channeladvisor.com/images/channeladvisor/channeladvisor_po